<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#1e3b36">
  <title>德累斯顿精品店德语</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #172420;
      --muted: #60716c;
      --paper: #f6f2ea;
      --card: #fffdf8;
      --sage: #dce8de;
      --pine: #1e3b36;
      --pine-2: #295148;
      --gold: #c68137;
      --line: #d9ddd3;
      --red: #9c3c35;
      --shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(23, 36, 32, .08);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { margin: 0; background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif; line-height: 1.55; }
    button, input { font: inherit; }
    button { cursor: pointer; }
    .top { background: var(--pine); color: white; padding: 44px max(24px, calc((100% - 1120px)/2)); }
    .eyebrow { margin: 0 0 10px; color: #d9e6d6; font-size: .82rem; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    h1 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.55rem); letter-spacing: -.045em; line-height: 1.04; }
    .subtitle { max-width: 760px; margin: 17px 0 0; color: #e5ece4; font-size: 1.04rem; }
    .nav { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 5; display: flex; gap: 8px; overflow: auto; padding: 10px max(16px, calc((100% - 1120px)/2)); background: rgba(255,253,248,.94); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); }
    .nav a, .chip { flex: 0 0 auto; padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 999px; color: var(--pine); text-decoration: none; font-size: .9rem; background: white; }
    .nav a:hover, .chip.active { background: var(--pine); border-color: var(--pine); color: white; }
    main { max-width: 1120px; margin: auto; padding: 28px 20px 64px; }
    section { scroll-margin-top: 68px; margin-top: 42px; }
    .section-title { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: end; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h2 { margin: 0; color: var(--pine); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); letter-spacing: -.03em; }
    h3 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .small, .hint { color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
    .panel { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 18px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); padding: clamp(18px, 4vw, 28px); }
    .overview { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.25fr .75fr; gap: 18px; }
    .notice { border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); background: #fff7e9; padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; }
    .notice p { margin: 0; }
    .plan-list { margin: 14px 0 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .plan-list li + li { margin-top: 7px; }
    .progress-wrap { display: grid; place-items: center; min-height: 210px; text-align: center; }
    .ring { --p: 0; display: grid; place-items: center; width: 142px; height: 142px; border-radius: 50%; background: conic-gradient(var(--gold) calc(var(--p) * 1%), #e6e9df 0); }
    .ring-inner { display: grid; place-items: center; width: 112px; height: 112px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--card); }
    .ring strong { color: var(--pine); font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .day-controls { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .day-controls button, .primary, .secondary { border: 0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .day-controls button, .secondary { color: var(--pine); background: var(--sage); }
    .primary { color: white; background: var(--pine); }
    .day-controls button:hover, .secondary:hover { background: #c6dbc9; }
    .primary:hover { background: var(--pine-2); }
    .today-meta { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .metric { padding: 12px; background: #f4f7f1; border-radius: 12px; }
    .metric strong { display: block; color: var(--pine); }
    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
    .vocab-card { position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 268px; padding: 17px; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 7px 19px rgba(23,36,32,.045); }
    .vocab-card.done { border-color: #7caf81; background: #fbfefa; }
    .card-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px; align-items: start; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 8px; background: #e9f0e7; color: var(--pine); border-radius: 999px; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .term-button { display: block; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0 2px; padding: 0; border: 0; color: var(--pine); background: transparent; text-align: left; font-size: 1.24rem; font-weight: 750; line-height: 1.25; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .term-button:hover, .term-button:focus-visible { color: var(--gold); outline: none; }
    .term-button::after { content: ' 🔊'; font-size: .72rem; vertical-align: middle; opacity: .7; }
    .plural { color: var(--muted); font-size: .86rem; }
    .translation { margin: 10px 0 7px; font-weight: 700; }
    .sentence { margin: 8px 0 0; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed var(--line); font-size: .94rem; }
    .sentence em { display: block; margin-top: 3px; color: var(--muted); font-style: normal; font-size: .86rem; }
    .extra-examples { margin: 9px 0 0; padding: 9px 0 0; border-top: 1px dashed var(--line); font-size: .86rem; }
    .extra-examples p { margin: 0 0 7px; }
    .extra-examples p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .extra-examples em { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-style: normal; font-size: .82rem; }
    @media (hover: hover) {
      .vocab-card:not(:hover):not(:focus-within):not(.show-translation) .translation,
      .vocab-card:not(:hover):not(:focus-within):not(.show-translation) .sentence em,
      .vocab-card:not(:hover):not(:focus-within):not(.show-translation) .extra-examples { display: none; }
    }
    .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 7px; margin-top: auto; padding-top: 12px; }
    .actions button, .actions a { padding: 7px 9px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--pine); background: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 650; }
    .actions button:hover, .actions a:hover { background: var(--sage); }
    .actions .done-btn { margin-left: auto; }
    .filters { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin: 14px 0; }
    .search-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
    #search { width: min(100%, 460px); padding: 11px 13px; background: white; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; outline-color: var(--gold); }
    .grammar-grid, .roadmap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
    .grammar-card, .road-card { padding: 18px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; background: var(--card); }
    .grammar-card .example { color: var(--pine); font-weight: 700; }
    .grammar-card .example + p { margin-top: 5px; }
    .week { color: var(--gold); font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .06em; }
    .pronunciation { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr; gap: 18px; }
    .number-lab { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr .9fr; gap: 18px; }
    .number-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .number-grid button { min-width: 48px; padding: 9px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 9px; background: white; color: var(--pine); font-weight: 750; }
    .number-grid button:hover { background: var(--sage); }
    .price-box { padding: 20px; border-radius: 14px; color: white; background: var(--pine); text-align: center; }
    .price-box strong { display: block; margin: 8px 0; font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.4rem); letter-spacing: -.04em; }
    .tutor-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 260px; gap: 18px; }
    .chat-log { min-height: 380px; max-height: 560px; overflow-y: auto; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; background: #f8faf5; }
    .chat-message { max-width: 88%; margin: 8px 0; padding: 11px 12px; border-radius: 14px; background: white; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .chat-message.user { margin-left: auto; color: white; background: var(--pine); border-color: var(--pine); border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; }
    .chat-message.teacher { border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; }
    .chat-de { font-weight: 700; color: var(--pine); }
    .chat-message.user .chat-de { color: white; }
    .chat-zh, .chat-tip { margin-top: 4px; font-size: .84rem; }
    .chat-zh { color: var(--muted); }
    .chat-tip { color: #78603d; }
    .chat-message.user .chat-zh { color: #d9e6d6; }
    .speak-small { float: right; padding: 2px 6px; border: 0; border-radius: 6px; color: var(--pine); background: var(--sage); font-size: .76rem; }
    .chat-form { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .chat-form input { min-width: 0; flex: 1; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; outline-color: var(--gold); }
    .scenario-list { display: grid; align-content: start; gap: 8px; }
    .scenario-list button { padding: 11px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; color: var(--pine); background: white; text-align: left; font-weight: 700; }
    .scenario-list button:hover, .scenario-list button.active { color: white; background: var(--pine); border-color: var(--pine); }
    .dw-routine { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px; margin: 14px 0 18px; }
    .dw-step { padding: 12px; border-radius: 11px; background: #f4f7f1; }
    .dw-step strong { display: block; color: var(--pine); }
    .dw-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
    .dw-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 240px; padding: 17px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 15px; background: var(--card); }
    .dw-card.done { border-color: #7caf81; background: #fbfefa; }
    .dw-level { color: var(--gold); font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .08em; }
    .dw-card p { margin: 7px 0; font-size: .9rem; }
    .dw-card .actions { margin-top: auto; }
    .sound-list { display: grid; gap: 9px; }
    .sound { padding: 10px 12px; background: #f4f7f1; border-radius: 10px; }
    .sound strong { color: var(--pine); }
    .resource-list { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
    .resource { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink); background: white; }
    .resource:hover { border-color: var(--pine); }
    .resource b { color: var(--pine); }
    .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: .85rem; }
    .toast { position: fixed; left: 50%; bottom: 22px; z-index: 20; transform: translate(-50%, 130px); padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--pine); color: white; box-shadow: var(--shadow); transition: transform .25s ease; font-size: .9rem; }
    .toast.show { transform: translate(-50%, 0); }
    @media (max-width: 850px) { .overview, .pronunciation, .number-lab, .tutor-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .cards, .dw-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); } .grammar-grid, .roadmap { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } .dw-routine { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    @media (max-width: 540px) { .top { padding-top: 34px; } main { padding-inline: 14px; } .cards, .dw-grid, .grammar-grid, .roadmap, .dw-routine { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .today-meta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .vocab-card { min-height: 234px; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="top">
    <p class="eyebrow">Dresden · Boutique · Alltag</p>
    <h1>德累斯顿精品店德语</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">只学你在街上、商场和店里马上会用到的德语。每个词都绑定中文、完整句子、语法提示与一键朗读。</p>
  </header>
  <nav class="nav" aria-label="页面导航">
    <a href="#dw">DW教材</a><a href="#today">今天学习</a><a href="#teacher">小老师</a><a href="#numbers">数字金额</a><a href="#vocabulary">单词库</a><a href="#grammar">语法</a><a href="#roadmap">路线图</a><a href="#pronunciation">发音</a>
  </nav>
  <main>
    <section class="overview" aria-label="学习说明">
      <div class="panel">
        <h2>先开口，再精确</h2>
        <p>你的目标是日常生活与精品店经营沟通，不是考试。词汇一律按“<strong>名词 + 复数 + 场景句</strong>”记忆，顾客对话优先使用礼貌的 <strong>Sie</strong>。</p>
        <div class="notice"><p><strong>对原方案的三处调整：</strong>先学标准德语，萨克森方言放在 A2 之后；冠词不能完全跳过，但不要求一开始背得完美；3 个月可胜任基础接待，合同、税务和高风险谈判仍应请专业人士核对。</p></div>
        <ul class="plan-list">
          <li>第 1 月：每天 40 分钟——生存场景、数字、礼貌提问、发音。</li>
          <li>第 2–3 月：每天 60 分钟——产品介绍、售后、补货、租铺沟通。</li>
          <li>第 4–6 月：每周实战 2 次——供应商、社交、小型谈判与书面消息。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="panel progress-wrap">
        <div class="ring" id="ring"><div class="ring-inner"><strong id="progressNumber">0%</strong><span class="small">已掌握</span></div></div>
        <p class="small">点击“会了”保存进度；数据只保存在这台设备的浏览器里。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="dw">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>DW《Nicos Weg》主教材路线</h2><p class="hint">DW 负责系统输入与听力；本网站负责你的精品店词汇、数字、发音和主动开口。每完成一个 DW 单元，就完成下面相应的实战任务。</p></div></div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="dw-routine"><div class="dw-step"><strong>① 20 分钟</strong><span class="small">看 DW 视频，先不看字幕。</span></div><div class="dw-step"><strong>② 15 分钟</strong><span class="small">完成 DW 单元练习。</span></div><div class="dw-step"><strong>③ 15 分钟</strong><span class="small">在本站复习对应词卡。</span></div><div class="dw-step"><strong>④ 10 分钟</strong><span class="small">用小老师完成一轮对话。</span></div></div>
        <div class="notice"><p><strong>使用方法：</strong>点击每张卡的“打开 DW”，从对应主题开始。DW 课程覆盖 A1–B1；你先按下列 12 个 A1 实战单元推进，不必一次看完整部课程。</p></div>
        <div id="dwCards" class="dw-grid" style="margin-top:16px"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="today">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>今天学习</h2><p class="hint">每天 6–8 张卡。先听、再跟读、再说出自己的版本。</p></div></div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="day-controls"><button id="prevDay" type="button">← 前一天</button><strong id="dayTitle">第 1 天</strong><button id="nextDay" type="button">后一天 →</button></div>
        <p id="dayFocus"></p>
        <div class="today-meta"><div class="metric"><strong id="morning">早上 15 分钟</strong><span class="small">词卡 + 朗读</span></div><div class="metric"><strong id="evening">晚上 25 分钟</strong><span class="small">情景跟读 + 录音</span></div><div class="metric"><strong id="task">实战任务</strong><span class="small">今天就用一次</span></div></div>
        <div class="cards" id="todayCards"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="numbers">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>数字、价格与金额</h2><p class="hint">数字要单独练：先点数字听读法，再练价格、日期和电话号码。</p></div></div>
      <div class="panel number-lab">
        <div>
          <h3>先记住这些关键数字</h3>
          <div class="number-grid" id="numberGrid"></div>
          <p class="hint">规律：21 = <strong>einundzwanzig</strong>（先说“1 和”，再说“20”）；47 = <strong>siebenundvierzig</strong>。价格 12,50 € 读作 <strong>zwölf Euro fünfzig</strong>。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="price-box"><span>随机价格练习</span><strong id="priceDisplay">12,50 €</strong><button id="speakPrice" class="secondary" type="button">听读法</button> <button id="newPrice" class="secondary" type="button">换一个</button><p id="priceWords" style="margin:12px 0 0;color:#e5ece4"></p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="teacher">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>德语小老师</h2><p class="hint">选择一个情景，用德语回复老师。它会给出下一句、中文提示和常见表达纠正；点击老师的话可朗读。</p></div></div>
      <div class="panel tutor-layout">
        <div>
          <div id="chatLog" class="chat-log" aria-live="polite"></div>
          <form id="tutorForm" class="chat-form"><input id="tutorInput" autocomplete="off" placeholder="用德语输入你的回答，例如：Ich heiße Matteo."><button class="primary" type="submit">发送</button></form>
        </div>
        <aside class="scenario-list" aria-label="对话情景"><span class="small">选择练习场景</span><button type="button" data-scenario="intro">① 自我介绍</button><button type="button" data-scenario="store">② 店铺接待</button><button type="button" data-scenario="price">③ 报价与付款</button><button type="button" data-scenario="directions">④ 问路</button><button type="button" data-scenario="free">⑤ 自由练一句</button><p class="hint">这是离线情景老师，适合把基础句练成反应；开放式长对话需要接入 AI 服务。</p></aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="vocabulary">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>精品店与生活单词库</h2><p class="hint">悬停词卡直接显示中文；点击德语词只读这个词。未收录的词可直接在线查词。</p></div><span id="resultCount" class="small"></span></div>
      <div class="search-row"><input id="search" type="search" placeholder="搜索中文、德语或例句，例如：气球 / Rabatt / Geschenk"><button id="onlineLookup" class="secondary" type="button">在线查这个词 ↗</button></div>
      <div class="filters" id="filters"></div>
      <div class="cards" id="allCards"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="grammar">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>只学马上能用的语法</h2><p class="hint">语法不是背规则比赛；每条规则都要替换成你的产品和店铺信息说三次。</p></div></div>
      <div class="grammar-grid" id="grammarCards"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="roadmap">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>12 周开口路线</h2><p class="hint">每周六复习，周日录一段 1–3 分钟的德语。不要跳到方言或复杂合同。</p></div></div>
      <div class="roadmap" id="roadmapCards"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="pronunciation">
      <div class="section-title"><div><h2>发音与真人输入</h2><p class="hint">前期练标准德语（Hochdeutsch）。萨克森口音可先听懂，不必刻意模仿。</p></div></div>
      <div class="panel pronunciation">
        <div>
          <h3>中文学习者优先避坑</h3>
          <div class="sound-list">
            <div class="sound"><strong>z = /ts/</strong>：<em>Zeit, zehn</em>，像“茨”，不是英语 z。</div>
            <div class="sound"><strong>w = /v/；v 常 = /f/</strong>：<em>wo, Wasser; Vater</em>。</div>
            <div class="sound"><strong>sch = /ʃ/；词首 sp/st</strong>：<em>Schule; Sport; Straße</em>。</div>
            <div class="sound"><strong>ü / ö</strong>：先做圆唇，再分别试着说“衣 / 诶”；不要直接读成“乌 / 欧”。</div>
            <div class="sound"><strong>ch</strong>：<em>ich</em> 的 <em>ch</em> 轻而靠前；<em>Buch</em> 的 <em>ch</em> 靠后，像轻擦气。</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>每句 4 步法</h3>
          <ol class="plan-list"><li>不看文字听原句 2 次。</li><li>看德语文本，按短语停顿跟读。</li><li>和原声同时说一遍；先保节奏，不逐字硬读。</li><li>录下自己，再比对一个问题：元音、重音或语速。</li></ol>
          <div class="resource-list" style="margin-top:16px">
